description: We have high-end finishes in our stunning apartments. We have beautiful views from our rooftop terrace. We have fun and functional spaces for your pets. We have a sparkling saltwater pool and four distinct courtyards that make it easy to enjoy the San Diego sunshine. We have an incredible location in West Mission Valley across from Fashion Valley Mall. All that's missing from our luxury apartments in Fashion Valley is you! We're taking luxury living in Mission Valley to the next level with our brand new studio, 1 and 2 bedroom apartments. Each home offers a spacious layout with plenty of room to embrace your passion and in-demand amenities like a full-sized washer and dryer, USB outlets in the living areas, and a kitchen pantry. With form, function, and convenience all in one place, life comes together naturally at Rivair!
